{"tid":808614,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"DICE：的Radeon顯卡無緣享用“戰地5”的實時光追","createTime":"2018-09-06T12:50:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-08T07:51:42.000Z","uid":202301,"like":3,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"0768b9eba8773f132e9dac863870fed317a0008a","tid":808614,"uid":202301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T12:50:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mydrivers.com/newsview/593805.html?ref=\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mydrivers.com%2Fnewsview%2F593805.html%3Fref%3D&d=33ZlhKVvrwGLRFUT9hC9Cf755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=f0136d9f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mydrivers.com/newsview/593805.html?ref=</a><br />\n<br />\nlink內原文殘體字注意<br />\n=====================<br />\n儘管遊戲開發者們透露，NVIDIA正在將&ldquo;實時光線追踪&rdquo;技術確立為一種開放標準，但至少現在而言，的Radeon顯卡想要享用，還不現實。<br />\n<br />\n據&ldquo;戰地V&rdquo;開發商DICE的技術指導Christian Holmquist介紹，他們目前僅做了基於DXR API和NVIDIA硬件的優化工作，很多代碼具有依附性，如果換了平台就無法很好地運行。<br />\n<br />\n我們知道，AMD的Radeon的顯卡並沒有關於實時光追的專門計算架構，可能在效率和效果上會大打折扣。<br />\n<br />\n不過DICE表示，新寒霜引擎下的&ldquo;戰地V&rdquo;在DX12下的表現和&ldquo;戰地1&rdquo;一樣好。<br />\n<br />\n另外，基督教還坦言，開啟實時光追後，CPU多線程的調用量也加大了，預計&ldquo;戰地V&rdquo;定稿的最低配置和推薦配置都要比前作高一些。當然，他強調，更依賴多核多線程是大勢所趨，且對用戶來說，比更高的單核頻率實現起來要容易很多。<br />\n===================<br />\n<br />\n有睇過nvidia發佈會都知開咗rtx 之後lag到得返60fps 都冇，係打機嘅都唔會開住嚟玩(除非你開game 係為咗睇景)<br />\n<br />\n再者rtx2000系列啲卡嘅價錢.....<br />\n同埋2080個性能都唔係勁過1080ti 好多，畀著你會唔會專門為rtx 而花大錢開game 睇景(注意係睇景唔係打機)？<br />\n<br />\n有廠商肯採用rtx 同推廣呢個新技術係好事，但係好似DICE 咁特登寸9 AMD 真係唔知用意何在<br />\n<br />\n唔好唔記得AMD 今年3月已經喺GPUopen 講明會搞光線追蹤<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.amd.com/zh-hant/technologies/radeon-rays\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amd.com%2Fzh-hant%2Ftechnologies%2Fradeon-rays&d=33ZlhKVvrwGLRFUT9hC9Cf755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=a58f0be2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.amd.com/zh-hant/technologies/radeon-rays</a><br />\n<br />\n留名AMD今年年尾嘅7nm gpu 反打一波"},{"pid":"912a30330a5a6a473ea63446c83ca14f24027b32","tid":808614,"uid":36128,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T17:20:48.000Z","msg":"開完個位數fps 你打埋我個份 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"869f2da5de607cfaa20170c09460dcbd5fd21b3b","tid":808614,"uid":42469,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T17:57:25.000Z","msg":"AAA遊戲其中一個特色唔係就係靚景咩，講到為睇景好出奇咁"},{"pid":"fd16421dc15630307a5fe5459df0e3ea3e0ebe65","tid":808614,"uid":35542,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T18:11:18.000Z","msg":"AMD而家係咪無同DICE合作？<br />\nDICE之前幫AMD手一齊整Mantle<br />\n之後AMD將Mantle捐贈衍生咗Vulkan<br />\n但DICE又無喺game支援Vulkan<br />\n而家同nvidia一齊搞Ray tracing"},{"pid":"34ea716b57b162bfee7be93d62b8a6f2aa757dcb","tid":808614,"uid":88826,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"fd16421dc15630307a5fe5459df0e3ea3e0ebe65","tid":808614,"uid":35542,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T18:11:18.000Z","msg":"AMD而家係咪無同DICE合作？<br />\nDICE之前幫AMD手一齊整Mantle<br />\n之後AMD將Mantle捐贈衍生咗Vulkan<br />\n但DICE又無喺game支援Vulkan<br />\n而家同nvidia一齊搞Ray tracing"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T18:28:59.000Z","msg":"Ray tracing 係用 DXR 既 API<br />\n<br />\n佢優化 N 記無可口非，市面上係得一張卡有專門處理 RT"},{"pid":"e0406be1e3d2fb3ff952a97c709494ee5ad4dba4","tid":808614,"uid":54574,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T23:46:33.000Z","msg":"基督教還坦言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db9865e602bce57cf5a6423acb3050a363696ec9","tid":808614,"uid":195761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"34ea716b57b162bfee7be93d62b8a6f2aa757dcb","tid":808614,"uid":88826,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"fd16421dc15630307a5fe5459df0e3ea3e0ebe65","tid":808614,"uid":35542,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T18:11:18.000Z","msg":"AMD而家係咪無同DICE合作？<br />\nDICE之前幫AMD手一齊整Mantle<br />\n之後AMD將Mantle捐贈衍生咗Vulkan<br />\n但DICE又無喺game支援Vulkan<br />\n而家同nvidia一齊搞Ray tracing